  <description><![CDATA[<p>Are you looking for an adventure or do you just want to relax on the mountain side? In Livigno, you don't have to choose! Located in a valley close to the Swiss border it's the perfect place to head if you want to spend your holiday reconnecting with nature - you'll be surrounded by mountains, lakes, forests and panoramic views.</p>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">What to see on a Livigno holiday</h3>
<p>In the Summer there's plenty of opportunity for hiking and adrenaline filled mountain biking. The Forcola pass links <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a> to <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> - which means you can cross the boarder and explore trails over there too. You can go paddle boarding on Livigno Lake or even test your agility at one of Livigno's adventure parks. What we love to do is morning yoga on the mountain, surrounded by stunning views of the valley. It's the best way to find your inner zen! If wildlife is your thing, then look out for the Ibex and Wild Eagles.</p>
<p>The food here isn't typically Italian, instead it's based on the flavours and cooking styles found in the valley. You'll get to try delicious local mountain dishes which are usually made from rich meats, and local cheeses - these dishes are bound to set you up for an action packed day exploring the mountains.</p>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Why book a Livigno holiday with Inghams</h3>
<p>We work with Livigno all year round and have great connections with local hotels and activity centres. You'll never be left wondering what to do next with the fantastic staff in our hand-picked hotels, who are always happy to help. You'll be able to tailor your adventures to exactly what you like, all the while knowing you're in <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">safe hands</a></strong> with Inghams.</p>]]></description>
